                  <span class="text-lg">Pitching this proposal to my professors</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                  <span class="text-arc-electric text-2xl mt-1">‚Üí</span>
                  <span class="text-lg">Designing the experiments</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                  <span class="text-arc-electric text-2xl mt-1">‚Üí</span>
                  <span class="text-lg">Sharing information with my supervisory team</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                  <span class="text-arc-electric text-2xl mt-1">‚Üí</span>
                  <span class="text-lg">Negotiating intellectual property terms with my university</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <p class="text-lg">
                There's <strong class="text-white text-2xl">no lab yet</strong>. No funding. No team. No published results.
              </p>
              <div class="pt-6 border-t border-gray-700/50">
