            Build Something<br/>Similar?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Love the approach but want to apply it to your own field? You don't need to contribute to arc^.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Take these tools:</p>
