              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
                <span class="text-living-earth text-xl">‚Üí</span>
                <span><strong>Re:Practise Framework</strong> (ethics model)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
                <span class="text-living-earth text-xl">‚Üí</span>
                <span><strong>arc^ GitHub</strong> (codebase)</span>
              </li>
