            Explore Re:Practise ‚Üó
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Path B -->
        <div class="bg-arc-electric/5 border-2 border-arc-electric/30 rounded-2xl p-10 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-arc-electric/20 transition-all duration-300 group">
          <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-arc-electric mb-6 font-mono leading-tight">
            Contribute<br/>to arc^?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
