            <span class="text-4xl">üî¨</span> Researchers
          </h3>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl">
            Validate, replicate, and co-develop early frameworks. Your expertise shapes responsible methods for plasma-water research. Emerging questions await your scrutiny.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Practitioners -->
        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-8 py-4 hover:pl-12 transition-all duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-4 font-mono flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="text-4xl">üåç</span> Practitioners
          </h3>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl">
            Apply arc^ technologies locally under shared safety standards while contributing to the commons. Projects remain locally governed but strengthen collective knowledge.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Reflection Questions - Open Space -->
      <div class="pt-16 border-t border-gray-700/50">
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white font-mono mb-12 leading-tight">
