        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Safety & Ethics - 2 Column -->
      <div class="mb-20 pb-16 border-b border-gray-700/50">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-living-earth font-mono mb-4">Safety & Ethics</h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mb-10">
          Every decision passes through four lenses: <span class="text-white">people, organisms, ecosystems, and future.</span>
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white font-mono mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-4xl">üë•</span> People
