        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-yellow-400 pl-6 py-3">
            <div class="text-xl font-bold text-yellow-400 font-mono mb-2">Hardware</div>
            <div class="text-base text-gray-400">
              <strong class="text-white">CERN-OHL-S v2</strong> ‚Ä¢ Designs, CAD files, specs ‚Ä¢ Modifications stay open
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-green-400 pl-6 py-3">
            <div class="text-xl font-bold text-green-400 font-mono mb-2">Documentation</div>
            <div class="text-base text-gray-400">
